params.sqlcmd: "select " +" M_CUST.\\"CUST_CD\\" as \\"CUST_CD\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"CUST_NAME\\" as \\"CUST_NAME\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"CUR_CD\\" as \\"CUR_CD\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"PRICE_ROUND_TYP\\" as \\"PRICE_ROUND_TYP\\", " +" M_CUR.\\"CUR_NAME\\" as \\"CUR_NAME\\", " +" M_CUR.\\"DECIMAL_FIG\\" as \\"DECIMAL_FIG\\" " +"from " +" M_CUST, " +" M_CUR " +"where " +" M_CUST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_CUST.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_CUST.\\"CUR_CD\\" = M_CUR.\\"CUR_CD\\"(+)"

"select " +" A.\\"UNIT_COST\\" as \\"UNIT_COST\\", " +" TO_CHAR(A.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE, " +" A.\\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\" as UNIT_COST_TYP, " +" A.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as MODIFY_COUNT " +"from " +" M_UNIT_COST A " +"where " +" A.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and A.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ? " +" and A.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"

"update " +" M_UNIT_COST " +"set " +" \\"UNIT_COST\\" = ?, " +" \\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\" = ? " +"where " +" M_UNIT_COST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_UNIT_COST.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_UNIT_COST.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_UNIT_COST.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_UNIT_COST " +"where " +" M_UNIT_COST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_UNIT_COST.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_UNIT_COST.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\" = ? " +"for update nowait"

"select " +" M_UNIT_COST.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_UNIT_COST " +"where " +" M_UNIT_COST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_UNIT_COST.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_UNIT_COST.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\" = ?"

"delete from " +" M_UNIT_COST " +"where " +" M_UNIT_COST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_UNIT_COST.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_UNIT_COST.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\" = ?"
"delete from " +" M_UNIT_COST " +"where " +" M_UNIT_COST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_UNIT_COST.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" COUNT(M_UNIT_COST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\") as \\"REC_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_UNIT_COST " +"where " +" M_UNIT_COST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_UNIT_COST.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_UNIT_COST.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_UNIT_COST " +"where " +" M_UNIT_COST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_UNIT_COST.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +"for update nowait"
"select " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"ITEM_NAME\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM " +"where " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" A.\\"UNIT_COST\\" AS \\"UNIT_COST\\", " +" A.\\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\" AS UNIT_COST_TYP " +"FROM " +" M_UNIT_COST A " +"WHERE " +" A.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" AND A.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ? " +" AND A.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND A.EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE = ?"
